text: Colobothea sublunulata is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Dmytro Zajciw in 1962. It is known from Bolivia.BioLib.cz - Colobothea sublunulata. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Colobotheini Category:Beetles described in 1962
title: Colobothea sublunulata
